{
  "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.68,
      "size": 26928,
      "text": "一个二阶矩阵，其实是一台改造平面的机器。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.84,
      "size": 45504,
      "text": "把它作用在一个单位正方形上，正方形会被拉伸、剪切，变成一个平行四边形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "而这个平行四边形有多大，就藏在一个熟悉的数里，它叫行列式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "area-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/area-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "矩阵的两列，正是变换后两条边向量。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "area-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/area-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "它们张成的平行四边形面积，恰好等于行列式的绝对值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "area",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "area-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/area-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "所以行列式告诉我们：面积被放大或缩小了多少倍。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "sign",
      "line_id": "sign-1",
      "filename": "sign-sign-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/sign-sign-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.62,
      "size": 25920,
      "text": "行列式还带着正负号，这个符号很有意思。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "sign",
      "line_id": "sign-2",
      "filename": "sign-sign-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/sign-sign-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "当它为负，说明平面被翻了个面，就像照镜子一样定向反转。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "sign",
      "line_id": "sign-3",
      "filename": "sign-sign-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/sign-sign-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.68,
      "size": 26928,
      "text": "正号保持原来的方向，负号则把左右手互换。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "zero",
      "line_id": "zero-1",
      "filename": "zero-zero-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/zero-zero-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "如果两列向量共线，平行四边形就被压成一条线段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "zero",
      "line_id": "zero-2",
      "filename": "zero-zero-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/zero-zero-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.68,
      "size": 42912,
      "text": "面积归零，行列式也就等于零，二维被压扁成一维，空间降维了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "拖动矩阵的四个元素，观察平行四边形如何随之伸缩变形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "试着让它翻转，或者压成一条线，看看行列式的数值怎么变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "行列式的绝对值是面积或体积的缩放因子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "它的符号记录着定向，为零则意味着降维。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "determinant-geometry",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/determinant-geometry/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "一个数,读懂了整个变换的几何,我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 32.66,
  "total_size": 523008
}